      <div class="text-5xl mb-4">ğŸ“²</div>
      <h3 class="font-display text-xl text-skate-accent mb-2">2. Download GPX</h3>
      <p class="text-sm text-skate-text-secondary">Grab the GPX file for turn-by-turn navigation on your phone. Works offline so you never lose your way.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="text-center">
      <div class="text-5xl mb-4">ğŸ›¹</div>
